---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About You - TORVIX Toronto">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="flex-grow pt-32 lg:pt-40 min-h-screen bg-[#f9f8f6]">
    
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center reveal">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-8 tracking-tight">
          About <span class="italic font-light">You.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed tracking-wide font-sans">
          You expect more than just a beautiful space. You expect a process that respects your time, your peace of mind, and your standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 border-t border-slate-200 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        
        <div class="space-y-24">
          <!-- Point 1 -->
          <div class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6">You Value Your Time</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide">
              Time is your most precious asset. You do not want to micromanage contractors, decipher confusing invoices, or chase down updates. You require a firm that operates autonomously, providing clear status reports while flawlessly managing the logistics in the background. You expect the project finished on time, every time.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Point 2 -->
          <div class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6">You Demand Turnkey Execution</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide">
              You aren't looking for a builder; you are looking for a partner to engineer a complete, turnkey transformation. You want to hand over the keys and return to an immaculate, move-in-ready space. From the initial demolition to the final architectural cleaning, you expect every microscopic detail to be handled with professional care.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Point 3 -->
          <div class="reveal">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6">You Seek a Stress-Free Experience</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide">
              Construction is notoriously stressful. You want the opposite. You desire a serene, highly organized process governed by utmost politeness and respect for your property. You expect a clean job site, respectful craftsmen, and radical honesty regarding every phase of the build.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-32 bg-[#f9f8f6] border-t border-slate-200 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-8 tracking-tight">We built TORVIX for you.</h2>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 bg-[#1a1a1a] text-white font-medium font-sans tracking-widest uppercase text-sm rounded-none hover:bg-slate-800 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out">
          Let's Begin
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
